quran[96]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,Jab woh honay wala waqia pesh aa jayega
  56,2,To koi uske waquh(occurrence) ko jhutlane wala na hoga
  56,3,Woh tah-o-bala (pasth aur buland) kardene wali aafat hogi
  56,4,Zameen us waqt ek baar hi hila daali jayegi
  56,5,Aur pahad is tarah reza reza kardiye jayenge
  56,6,Ke paraganda (scattered) gubar (dust) ban kar reh jayenge
  56,7,Tum log us waqt teen girohon (jamaat) mein taqseem ho jaogey
  56,8,"Dayein bazu waley, so dayein bazu walon (ke khush-naseebi ) ka kya kehna"
  56,9,"Aur bayein bazu waley, to bayein bazu walon (ki badnasibi ka) kya thikana"
  56,10,Aur aagey waley to phir aagey waley hi hain
  56,11,Wahi to muqarrab (nearest to Allah) log hain
  56,12,Niyamat bhari jannaton mein rahengey
  56,13,Aglon mein se bahut hongey
  56,14,Aur pichlon mein se kam
  56,15,Murassasa takhaton par (On thrones decorated)
  56,16,Takiye lagaye aamne saamne baithengey
  56,17,Unki majlison mein abadi ladke sharab-e-chashma-e jaari se
  56,18,Labrez pyale aur kantar (jugs) aur saagar liye daudte phirte hongey
  56,19,Jisey pee kar na unka sar chakrayega na unki aqal mein fatur (drunkenness) aayega
  56,20,Aur woh unke saamne tarah tarah ke lazeez phal (fruits) pesh karengey jisey chahe chun le
  56,21,Aur parindon ke gosht pesh karenge ke jis parinde ka chahein istimal karein
  56,22,Aur unke liye khubsurat aankhon wali hoorein hongi
  56,23,Aisi haseen jaise chupa kar rakkhey huey moti
  56,24,Yeh sab kuch un aamal ki jaza ke taur par unhein milega jo woh duniya mein karte rahe thay
  56,25,Wahan woh koi behuda kalaam ya gunah ki baat na sunengey
  56,26,Jo baat bhi hogi theek theek hogi
  56,27,"Aur daayein bazu waley, daayein bazu walon ki khush nasibi ka kya kehna"
  56,28,Woh be-khaar (thornless) beriyon(lote trees)
  56,29,Aur teh bar teh chadey huey kelon (bananas)
  56,30,Aur door tak phayli hui chaaon (shadow)
  56,31,Aur har dum rawan (gushing) paani
  56,32,Aur kabhi khatam na honay waley
  56,33,Aur bay rok-tok milne waley ba-kasrat phalon (fruits)
  56,34,Aur unchi nishist gaahon (exalted thrones) mein hongay
  56,35,Unki biwiyon ko hum khaas taur par naye sirey se paida karengey
  56,36,Aur unhein bakira (virgins) bana dengey
  56,37,Apne shoharon ki aashik aur umar mein humsin (equal age)
  56,38,Yeh kuch daayein bazu walon ke liye hai
  56,39,Woh aglon mein se bahut hongey
  56,40,Aur pichlon mein se bhi bahut
  56,41,"Aur baayein (left) bazu wale, bayein bazu walon ki badnasibi ka kya puchna"
  56,42,Woh luu ki lapat (midst of scorching wind) aur khaulte (boiling) huey paani
  56,43,Aur kaalay dhuwon (smoke) ke saaye mein hongey
  56,44,Jo na thanda hoga na aaram de
  56,45,Yeh woh log hongey jo is anjaam ko pahunchne se pehle khush haal thay
  56,46,Aur gunaah-e-azeem par israr karte thay
  56,47,Kehte thay “kya jab hum mar kar khaak ho jayengey aur haddiyon ka panjar reh jayengey to phir utha khadey kiye jayenge
  56,48,Aur kya hamare woh baap dada bhi uthaye jayengey jo pehle guzar chuke hain?”
  56,49,"Aye Nabi in logon se kaho, yaqeenan agle aur pichle sab"
  56,50,Ek din zaroor jama kiye janey wale hain jiska waqt muqarrar kiya ja chuka hai
  56,51,Phir aey gumrahon aur jhutlane walon
  56,52,Tum shajar-e-zaqqum ki giza khane waley ho
  56,53,Usi se tum pait bharogey
  56,54,Aur upar se khaulta (boiling) hua paani
  56,55,Toans (thirst) lagey huey ount (camel) ki tarah piogey
  56,56,Yahi baayein walon ki ziyafat ka saamaan roz-e-jaza mein
  56,57,Humne tumhein paida kiya hai phir kyun tasdeek (confirm) nahin karte
  56,58,"Kabhi tumne gaur kiya, yeh nutfa (sperm) jo tum daltey ho"
  56,59,Usse baccha tum banate ho ya uske banane wale hum hain
  56,60,"Humne tumharey darmiyan maut ko takseem kiya hai, aur hum issey aajiz nahin hai"
  56,61,Ke tumhari shaklein badal dein aur kisi aisi shakal mein tumhein paida kardein jisko tum nahin jante
  56,62,"Apni pehli paidaish ko to tum jante ho, phir kyun sabaq nahin letay"
  56,63,"Kabhi tumne socha, yeh beej (seed) jo tum botey ho"
  56,64,Insey khetiyan tum ugatey ho ya unke ugane waley hum hain
  56,65,Hum chahein to un khetoun ko bhus (rubble) bana kar rakh dein aur tum tarah tarah ki baatein banate reh jao
  56,66,Ke hum par to ulti chatti pad gayi (Lo! we are laden with debt)
  56,67,Balke humarey to naseeb hi phootey huey hain
  56,68,"Kabhi tumne aankhein khol kar dekha, yeh paani jo tum peetey ho"
  56,69,Isey tumne baadal se barsaya hai ya iske barsane wale hum hain
  56,70,"Hum chahein to isey sakht khari(bitter) bana kar rakh dein, phir kyun tum shukar guzar nahin hotey"
  56,71,"Kabhi tumne khayal kiya, yeh aag jo tum sulgate ho"
  56,72,Iska darakht tum ne paida kiya hai ya iske paida karne wale hum hain
  56,73,Humne usko yaad-dihani(reminder) ka zariya aur haajat-mandon (needy) ke liye saaman-e-zeist (provision) banaya hai
  56,74,"Pas aey Nabi, apne Rubb-e-azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"
  56,75,"Pas nahin main kasam khata hoon taaron ke mawake (setting or the mansions, etc.) ki"
  56,76,Agar tum samjho to yeh bahut badi qasam hai
  56,77,Ke yeh ek buland paya Quran hai
  56,78,Ek mehfooz kitaab mein sabt (inscribed)
  56,79,Jisey mutahreen (pure) ke siwa koi choo nahin sakta
  56,80,Yeh Rubb-ul- Aalameen ka nazil karda hai
  56,81,Phir kya is kalam ke saath tum be-atnayi (indifferent) barat-te ho
  56,82,Aur is niyamat mein apna hissa tumne yeh rakkha hai ke isey jhutlate ho
  56,83,To jab marne wale ki jaan halaq tak pahunch chuki hoti hai
  56,84,Aur tum aankhon se dekh rahe hotey ho ke woh marr raha hai
  56,85,Us waqt tumhare ba-nisbat hum uske zyada kareeb hotey hain magar tumko nazar nahin aatey
  56,86,Ab agar tum kisi ke mahkoom(anyones authority) nahin ho aur apne is khayal mein sacchey ho
  56,87,Us waqt uski nikalti hui jaan ko wapas kyun nahin ley aatey
  56,88,Phir woh marne wala agar muqarrabin (near to Allah) mein se hon
  56,89,To uske liye rahat aur umda rizq aur niyamat bhari jannat hai
  56,90,Aur agar woh ashaab-e-yameen mei se ho
  56,91,"To uska istaqbal (welcome) yun hota hai ke salaam hai tujhey, tu ashab-ul-yameen (People on the Right) mein se hai"
  56,92,Aur agar woh jhutlane waley gumraah logon mein se ho
  56,93,To uski tawazu ke liye khaulta (boiling) pani hai
  56,94,Aur jahannum mein jhonka jaana
  56,95,Yeh sab kuch qataii haqq hai
  56,96,Pas aey Nabi apne Rubb-e-Azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo